183
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:38,640
Under-baked, and these delicate sponges will collapse. 

184
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:41,240
A challenge the bakers found tricky. 

185
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:45,960
Oh. It's all gone wrong. 

