196
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:30,120
- Don't want it too weak. 
- Mary, that's brutal!
- No, just right. 

197
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,320
OK, all I'm going to do is heat this up now. 

198
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:36,760
I can feel that that's actually all dissolved in there 

